        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill amends the Public Health Service Act to require the Department of Health and Human Services to use 20% of the appropriations for the Substance Abuse Prevention and Treatment Block Grant program to award grants to recovery community organizations to provide recovery-focused addiction treatment for individuals&nbsp;with a&nbsp;substance use disorder.</p>]]></text>
